Rulings.Cat:
● “Icarus Attack” targets 2 cards. Even if 1 of the target cards is a Spell/Trap and it is activated in a chain, both cards will still be destroyed.
● You can't choose “Icarus Attack” itself for 1 of its 2 targets.
